Difference between ptython 2 and 3:

****** In python2 print is a keyword and doesn't need parenthesis but in python3 print is a function and need a parenthesis.
****** In 2, there is one interger type but in 3 there is integer and long integer.
****** Code is not backward compatible from 2 to 3
****** 3 is a 10 years old package
****** For python3 in Mac and Windows, there is an editor available called Komodo.
****** In python, everything is an object.
	'Hello, world'.lower()'


******  ctrl + shift + r to run the code
****** ctrl + slash  to comment out any line
****** Inside print what we write is called print object

****** under class there could be functions. Sometimes functions are called methods, and variables inside a class is called properties. 

****** In python there is no difference between single quote or double quote


